OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry start with sunny spells,
OL,6,Fbut scattered showers developing for
OL,7,Fthe afternoon. Temperatures cooler
OL,8,Fthan yesterday for many, although
OL,9,Fsimilar in the far southeast
OL,10,Fespecially Kent, but still warm or
OL,11,Fvery warm overall.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny lingering showers moving
OL,14,Faway southeastwards, then a dry night
OL,15,Fwith clear spells. Overnight
OL,16,Ftemperatures rather fresher than of
OL,17,Flate in western parts, especially in
OL,18,Frural spots. Light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
