OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry with hazy sunshine and
OL,6,Fvery warm or hot for many again on
OL,7,FSaturday. Cooler near eastern coasts.
OL,8,
OL,9,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FTurning
OL,10,Fmore unsettled and cooler during the
OL,11,Fstart of next week. Temperatures
OL,12,Ffalling nearer normal for the time of
OL,13,Fyear. Becoming breezy with outbreaks
OL,14,Fof occasionally heavy rain or showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
